{"title":"Combined feed","url":"https://leoshcn.github.io/feeds/all.xml","elements":[{"title":"Lea Hinz (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Lea_Hinz\" title=\"Lea Hinz\">Lea Hinz</a></b> <i>(pictured)</i> gave up medical school to perform on the <a href=\"/wiki/Aerial_hoop\" title=\"Aerial hoop\">aerial hoop</a>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lea_Hinz","retrieved":1776755412875},{"title":"Temple of ECK (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that hundreds of residents of <a href=\"/wiki/Chanhassen,_Minnesota\" title=\"Chanhassen, Minnesota\">Chanhassen, Minnesota</a>, opposed the construction of the <b><a href=\"/wiki/Temple_of_ECK\" title=\"Temple of ECK\">Temple of ECK</a></b>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Temple_of_ECK","retrieved":1776755412876},{"title":"Carlos Quaremba (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that South Australian politician <b><a href=\"/wiki/Carlos_Quaremba\" title=\"Carlos Quaremba\">Carlos Quaremba</a></b> said of his childhood, \"I was the only <a href=\"/wiki/Wog\" title=\"Wog\">wog</a> in the whole school\"?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carlos_Quaremba","retrieved":1776755412946},{"title":"a Bronx bank building (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that, after <b><a href=\"/wiki/Dollar_Savings_Bank_Building\" title=\"Dollar Savings Bank Building\">a Bronx bank building</a></b><span class=\"nowrap\">'s</span> clock broke, people fired bullets towards it at night?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dollar_Savings_Bank_Building","retrieved":1776755412946},{"title":"2015 Mauritian municipal elections (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that Prime Minister <a href=\"/wiki/Anerood_Jugnauth\" title=\"Anerood Jugnauth\">Anerood Jugnauth</a> said municipal residents should be banned from voting if they refused to vote in the <b><a href=\"/wiki/2015_Mauritian_municipal_elections\" title=\"2015 Mauritian municipal elections\">2015 Mauritian municipal elections</a></b>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2015_Mauritian_municipal_elections","retrieved":1776755412948},{"title":"Gil Mains (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that American football player <b><a href=\"/wiki/Gil_Mains\" title=\"Gil Mains\">Gil Mains</a></b> flew feetfirst into opponents?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gil_Mains","retrieved":1776755412950},{"title":"giant root-rats (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that tunnels created by <b><a href=\"/wiki/Giant_root-rat\" title=\"Giant root-rat\">giant root-rats</a></b> can reach up to 34&nbsp;m (112&nbsp;ft) in length?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Giant_root-rat","retrieved":1776755412952},{"title":"Mowbray, Manitoba (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that some children from <a href=\"/wiki/North_Dakota\" title=\"North Dakota\">North Dakota</a> crossed the Canadian border daily to attend school in <b><a href=\"/wiki/Mowbray,_Manitoba\" title=\"Mowbray, Manitoba\">Mowbray, Manitoba</a></b>, in the early 1900s?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mowbray,_Manitoba","retrieved":1776755412954},{"title":"John Fasel (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that doctors removed six knives from <b><a href=\"/wiki/John_Fasel\" title=\"John Fasel\">John Fasel</a></b><span class=\"nowrap\">'s</span> stomach?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Fasel","retrieved":1776755412959},{"title":"Destination of the Month (Wikivoyage recommendations)","contents":"<style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r4523569\" typeof=\"mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion\" about=\"#mwt8\" data-mw=\"{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;templatestyles&quot;,&quot;attrs&quot;:{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;Banner/styles.css&quot;},&quot;parts&quot;:[{&quot;template&quot;:{&quot;target&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;banner&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;./Template:Banner&quot;},&quot;params&quot;:{&quot;direction&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;left&quot;},&quot;title&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;Pe